The Young Broker Network (YBN) was created to provide a mechanism for broker members (under 40) and those new to the industry (less than 5 years) to connect and build their professional capacity through education and industry involvement.

YBN Benefits:
- Opportunities to share ideas and perspectives specific to YBN activities;
- Participation in educational opportunities geared towards emerging professionals;
- Forge relationships within the insurance community;

Our company was founded in 2019 in accordance with the legislation of the Republic of Azerbaijan and obtained the special license as an insurance and reinsurance broker from the Chamber of Financial Market Supervision of the Republic of Azerbaijan.

“Buta broker” has been operating in the insurance market for almost 4 years and offering insurance services for all lines of insurances to multinational & local corporate/individual clients by cooperating closely with Azerbaijan Insurance Market and world’s leading insurance and reinsurance companies.

The mission of  BUTA Broker is:

– learning clients needs in insurance and reinsurance;

– working with personal and corporate clients and assisting people and businesses to manage risk and handle insurance claims;

–  determination of clients demands and offering them the mostoptimal insurance product;

–  giving a strong support to the network partners worldwide in this region.

We are proud of our close relationships with the world’s leading insurers and reinsurers, who offer innovative solutions to meet the needs of insurance and reinsurance, wherever they arise.

As a company we take great care of our clients. We also take great care to run a healthy business with strong solvency and no debt.

We design and deliver solutions that manage risk, optimize benefits, cultivate talent, and expand the power of capital to protect and strengthen institutions and individuals. Our unique perspective allows us to see the critical intersections between talent, assets and ideas — the dynamic formula that drives business performance.

